Note:
Runa Standard Library: Blockchain Virtual Machine Module

Provides comprehensive virtual machine implementation for smart contract execution.
Implements enterprise-grade VM capabilities with multi-architecture support, gas metering,
security sandboxing, and advanced execution features. Competitive with production VMs
in Ethereum (EVM), WebAssembly (WASM), and other leading blockchain virtual machines.

Features:
- Multi-architecture VM support (EVM, WASM, Custom bytecode)
- Gas metering and execution limits with precise accounting
- Security sandboxing and isolation mechanisms
- Stack-based and register-based execution models
- JIT compilation and optimization for performance
- Precompiled contracts and native function calls
- State access control and transaction context
- Exception handling and error recovery
- Memory management with bounds checking
- Call stack management and recursion limits
- Opcode execution with comprehensive instruction set
- Debug capabilities and execution tracing
- Contract deployment and upgrade mechanisms
- Cross-contract communication and message passing
- Deterministic execution for consensus compliance
:End Note

Note: Core VM Types
Type called "VirtualMachine":
    vm_type as VMType
    execution_engine as ExecutionEngine
    gas_meter as GasMeter
    memory_manager as MemoryManager
    stack_manager as StackManager
    state_interface as StateInterface
    security_manager as SecurityManager
    precompiled_contracts as PrecompiledContracts
    debug_interface as DebugInterface
    jit_compiler as JITCompiler
    call_stack as CallStack
    execution_context as ExecutionContext

Type VMType is:
    | ETHEREUM_VM
    | WEBASSEMBLY_VM
    | RUNA_VM
    | BITCOIN_SCRIPT_VM
    | CUSTOM_VM

Type called "ExecutionEngine":
    engine_type as EngineType
    instruction_set as InstructionSet
    opcode_handlers as Dictionary[Integer, OpcodeHandler]
    execution_stats as ExecutionStatistics
    optimization_level as OptimizationLevel

Type EngineType is:
    | INTERPRETER
    | JIT_COMPILER
    | AOT_COMPILER
    | HYBRID

Type called "GasMeter":
    gas_limit as Integer
    gas_used as Integer
    gas_price as Integer
    gas_schedule as GasSchedule
    refund_counter as Integer
    memory_gas_used as Integer
    storage_gas_used as Integer

Type called "GasSchedule":
    base_gas_costs as Dictionary[String, Integer]
    memory_gas_costs as MemoryGasCosts
    storage_gas_costs as StorageGasCosts
    call_gas_costs as CallGasCosts
    precompiled_gas_costs as Dictionary[String, Integer]

Type called "MemoryManager":
    memory_size as Integer
    max_memory_size as Integer
    memory_pages as List[MemoryPage]
    active_memory as List[Integer]
    memory_protection as MemoryProtection
    allocation_strategy as AllocationStrategy

Type called "MemoryPage":
    page_id as Integer
